POV: Your morning routine just got a major upgrade. 🤎

Designed for busy schedules and on-the-go mornings, Wink Stamp helps create a softer, wearable wing in record time. Now available in dark brown, it’s the perfect swap on the days a black wing feels too bold.

Available now in the @sephora app and on sephora.com 🛒

#kajabeauty #koreanbeauty #browneyeliner #everydaymakeup #sephora

Free-handing is a thing of the past. Achieve @nataliya_makeup’s sharp brown eyeliner look in just three simple steps:

✨ Stamp: Apply a ready-made wing to the outer corner of your lid using Wink Stamp.
✨ Line: Connect the wing across the lash line with our Brush Pen.
✨ Repeat: Mirror the same on the other eye.

That is the secret to perfect, symmetrical wings in seconds.

If you love our original black shade, you will love Wink Stamp Brown just as much. Available now in the @sephora app and on sephora.com.🤎
